data.description: A Beautiful Masterpiece- 3217 sq feet of living space all meticulously maintained! 4th bedroom possibility! Located on a 1.96 wooded lot w/a deep and sparkling POOL, Gazebo, and mature Landscape! A handsome entrance of brick and rod iron work leads you to a 2 car garage with storage AND an extra climate controlled space formerly used as a gym. On the main level you have a Jack and Jill wing with a half bath for guests, primary suite, large living room with Oak hardwood flooring & a large gas fireplace. The bright & spacious formal dining room leads into the eat-in kitchen with double ovens, deep sink, top of the line sink faucet and fridge, matching granite counters & backsplash, w/quality cabinetry- plenty of storage! Upstairs bonus, storage, full bath, & more- See photos for more remarks. This home is ready to create new memories! Located in established Druid Hills also known as the "Belle Meade of Dickson" this home is gorgeous. Sellers are ready to sell today! Open House Feb 17th
